00:05:21.912 --> 00:05:23.431
Where are you from?

00:05:24.071 --> 00:05:25.391
From where I came from.

00:05:26.071 --> 00:05:27.792
Where are you going?

00:05:28.552 --> 00:05:29.672
To where I should go.

00:05:30.391 --> 00:05:32.232
