00:05:33.831 --> 00:05:34.912
I'd like to know you.

00:05:35.511 --> 00:05:36.271
Miss.

00:05:36.831 --> 00:05:38.152
We're not destined to meet.

00:05:38.472 --> 00:05:39.032
You don't

00:05:39.112 --> 00:05:39.871
