00:05:40.672 --> 00:05:41.431
I don't care.

00:05:41.831 --> 00:05:43.912
Today, I'll make you my friend.

00:05:44.672 --> 00:05:45.871
Having fun chatting?

00:05:48.232 --> 00:05:49.552
I came at a bad time.

00:05:51.191 --> 00:05:52.152
Honey.

00:05:52.672 --> 00:05:53.431
Why are you here?

00:05:55.152 --> 00:05:55.912
You got me wrong.

00:06:01.311 --> 00:06:02.271
Who's your honey?

00:06:03.712 --> 00:06:05.871
Why so angry, Miss Feng?

00:06:09.271 --> 00:06:10.352
Am I angry?

00:06:10.912 --> 00:06:11.951
Or are you guilty?

00:06:13.592 --> 00:06:16.112
This is how I express admiration.

00:06:18.232 --> 00:06:19.712
You talk about admiration,

00:06:19.871 --> 00:06:20.751
but won't help me?

00:06:21.951 --> 00:06:22.631
Hypocrite.

00:06:22.992 --> 00:06:23.511
Miss Feng.

00:06:25.352 --> 00:06:26.751
I know you don't want to

00:06:26.992 --> 00:06:28.191
harm the innocent.

00:06:29.032 --> 00:06:30.311
But this is the border

00:06:30.431 --> 00:06:31.712
between Liang and Hua.

00:06:33.112 --> 00:06:34.191
Liang is seven days'

00:06:34.552 --> 00:06:35.391
travel away.

00:06:36.352 --> 00:06:38.152
We own estates there.

00:06:38.672 --> 00:06:39.472
No one can

00:06:40.112 --> 00:06:41.631
pressure you there.

00:06:43.071 --> 00:06:43.631
What?

00:06:45.071 --> 00:06:45.751
My father

00:06:46.032 --> 00:06:48.431
has been preparing for his retirement.

00:06:49.112 --> 00:06:50.552
That place seemed remote to me.

00:06:51.311 --> 00:06:52.352
But now I realize

00:06:52.631 --> 00:06:54.152
that it's all part of his plan.

00:06:55.391 --> 00:06:58.071
Escape with me.

00:07:03.992 --> 00:07:05.112
I must complete the task

00:07:07.112 --> 00:07:08.951
to dispel His Majesty's doubts.

00:07:09.511 --> 00:07:11.071
Only then will you truly be safe.

00:07:12.152 --> 00:07:13.191
