00:11:12.511 --> 00:11:13.472
No messengers.

00:11:14.151 --> 00:11:15.511
Especially not his son.

00:11:17.352 --> 00:11:19.671
You look extremely

00:11:20.352 --> 00:11:21.232
nervous.

00:11:22.312 --> 00:11:22.911
Have you

00:11:24.112 --> 00:11:24.952
found out about it?

00:11:27.192 --> 00:11:27.712
Yes.

00:11:29.312 --> 00:11:30.151
Father told me.

00:11:33.031 --> 00:11:33.511
Why

00:11:33.511 --> 00:11:34.911
didn't you tell me who you are?

00:11:37.271 --> 00:11:38.352
You're a prince.

00:11:38.511 --> 00:11:39.592
It's unfair that you

00:11:40.712 --> 00:11:41.551
have to hide.

00:11:42.751 --> 00:11:43.551
A prince?

00:11:47.031 --> 00:11:48.151
The former Crown Prince.

00:11:49.671 --> 00:11:51.072
It's shadier than being

00:11:52.031 --> 00:11:52.952
the illegitimate son.

00:11:53.871 --> 00:11:55.671
I deserve to die.

00:11:56.472 --> 00:11:57.631
That emperor deserves to die.

00:11:57.751 --> 00:11:58.352
Not you.

00:11:58.911 --> 00:11:59.712
Nonsense.

00:12:00.352 --> 00:12:01.391
Watch your tongue.

00:12:02.992 --> 00:12:03.871
I thought

00:12:05.192 --> 00:12:06.472
the Emperor's murderous intent

00:12:06.631 --> 00:12:07.671
was just a rumor.

00:12:08.271 --> 00:12:08.911
I didn't know

00:12:09.791 --> 00:12:11.671
that all the misfortunes
we've been through

00:12:12.271 --> 00:12:14.352
were orchestrated by him

00:12:14.592 --> 00:12:15.511
to eliminate us.

00:12:17.391 --> 00:12:18.952
Even with his throne so secure,

00:12:19.192 --> 00:12:19.871
he still targets

00:12:19.952 --> 00:12:21.511
a defenseless man.

00:12:22.151 --> 00:12:23.112
So inhuman.

00:12:23.871 --> 00:12:24.712
Victors reign.

00:12:25.751 --> 00:12:26.911
In his position,

00:12:27.592 --> 00:12:28.952
he can do as he pleases.

00:12:30.072 --> 00:12:30.671
Meanwhile,

00:12:32.072 --> 00:12:33.232
I must struggle to survive.

00:12:33.952 --> 00:12:35.592
I've let go of everything.

00:12:36.871 --> 00:12:37.312
Right.

00:12:38.551 --> 00:12:39.232
Does Father know

00:12:39.992 --> 00:12:40.832
about your visit?

00:12:42.312 --> 00:12:42.751
Yeah.

00:12:47.432 --> 00:12:49.232
I can tell you're rebellious.

00:12:49.631 --> 00:12:51.472
You must have come in secret,

00:12:51.992 --> 00:12:52.751
against his orders.

00:12:56.112 --> 00:12:56.511
Right.

00:12:57.551 --> 00:12:58.432
You said that

00:12:59.631 --> 00:13:01.352
you had been through a lot.

00:13:02.112 --> 00:13:03.551
Are you hanging in there?

00:13:05.511 --> 00:13:07.832
Father holds the title of Lord Dingyuan.

00:13:09.072 --> 00:13:10.712
We can withstand some petty tricks.

00:13:17.791 --> 00:13:18.911
Has your father decided

00:13:21.352 --> 00:13:22.352
to abandon me?

00:13:24.592 --> 00:13:27.271
We have plans in Liang.

00:13:28.592 --> 00:13:29.232
Come with me.

00:13:30.391 --> 00:13:31.671
Survival comes first.

00:13:36.232 --> 00:13:36.911
Lord Dingyuan

00:13:40.192 --> 00:13:41.511
is truly casting me aside?

00:13:45.271 --> 00:13:45.832
Youshou,

00:13:46.791 --> 00:13:48.031
my father has been

00:13:49.472 --> 00:13:50.751
bedridden for years.

00:13:51.671 --> 00:13:52.631
He's been exhausted

00:13:53.312 --> 00:13:54.391
by this matter.

00:13:55.271 --> 00:13:56.151
Don't blame him.

00:13:57.271 --> 00:13:58.271
How could I blame him?

00:13:59.472 --> 00:14:00.432
Without him,

00:14:01.072 --> 00:14:02.072
I would have died

00:14:02.312 --> 00:14:03.232
when I was seven.

00:14:10.271 --> 00:14:11.511
My whereabouts are exposed.

00:14:12.151 --> 00:14:14.072
Don't defy the authorities again

00:14:14.432 --> 00:14:15.391
by letting me escape.

00:14:16.192 --> 00:14:16.992
Turn me in.

00:14:17.712 --> 00:14:19.352
Earn merit for the Xue family.

00:14:20.072 --> 00:14:20.712
Are you crazy?

00:14:21.631 --> 00:14:22.671
After all these years,

00:14:23.871 --> 00:14:24.791
I'm tired of hiding.

00:14:25.832 --> 00:14:27.352
I'll sever all ties with the Xues.

00:14:28.271 --> 00:14:31.271
Let me satisfy that Emperor's wish

00:14:33.511 --> 00:14:34.232
and consider this

00:14:34.791 --> 00:14:36.232
repayment for your help.

00:14:38.472 --> 00:14:39.031
Youshou,

00:14:39.592 --> 00:14:41.192
don't let everything go to waste.

00:14:42.631 --> 00:14:43.391
Do you really think

00:14:43.671 --> 00:14:44.511
we'll be spared

00:14:45.271 --> 00:14:46.391
if we turn you in?

00:14:47.952 --> 00:14:49.511
He doesn't hesitate to kill

00:14:49.712 --> 00:14:50.631
his confidant.

00:14:51.352 --> 00:14:52.671
My father risked our family

00:14:52.952 --> 00:14:53.992
to protect you.

00:14:55.472 --> 00:14:56.551
If you do this,

00:14:57.911 --> 00:15:00.312
we'll be doomed together.

00:15:13.592 --> 00:15:14.312
(Traitor.)

00:15:15.312 --> 00:15:16.791
(Time to claim your life.)

00:15:18.791 --> 00:15:19.472
Miss Feng...

00:15:19.992 --> 00:15:20.472
How...

00:15:21.432 --> 00:15:22.551
You are Xue Youshou?

00:15:23.791 --> 00:15:25.031
Or should I call you

00:15:25.592 --> 00:15:26.952
Crown Prince Jia Xun?

00:15:31.511 --> 00:15:32.592
He's not the Crown Prince.

00:15:33.232 --> 00:15:34.791
He's just my half-brother.

00:15:36.551 --> 00:15:37.592
Xue Guardian Feng Zuoren

00:15:38.271 --> 00:15:39.151
is here to kill you.

00:15:40.432 --> 00:15:41.432
Any last words?

00:15:43.631 --> 00:15:44.472
You'll kill me?

00:15:46.592 --> 00:15:47.031
Don't.

00:16:09.112 --> 00:16:09.791
The jade pendant.

00:16:14.391 --> 00:16:15.151
You remember it.

00:16:16.312 --> 00:16:16.871
Feng.

00:16:24.871 --> 00:16:25.751
Young master.

00:16:28.151 --> 00:16:28.871
(Young master?)

00:16:37.112 --> 00:16:37.952
It's been so long.

00:16:40.551 --> 00:16:41.352
I never expected

00:16:43.112 --> 00:16:44.072
I'd see you again

00:16:47.911 --> 00:16:49.432
in this lifetime.

00:16:54.072 --> 00:16:55.432
After ten years,

00:16:58.631 --> 00:17:00.192
we reunited here of all places,

00:17:05.271 --> 00:17:06.632
but under such circumstances.

00:17:08.952 --> 00:17:09.432
Youshou,

00:17:11.031 --> 00:17:12.311
