Young master and Madam saved me

00:17:27.591 --> 00:17:28.872
and brought me home.

00:17:29.952 --> 00:17:30.912
I always thought

00:17:31.551 --> 00:17:32.632
that you were simply

00:17:32.912 --> 00:17:34.511
from a wealthy family.

00:17:51.071 --> 00:17:51.751
But you were

00:17:52.392 --> 00:17:54.872
the former Crown Prince
and she was the late Empress.

